0.2.7.name: atom-html-preview
0.2.7.description: A live preview tool for Atom Editor.
0.2.7.readme:
# Atom HTML Preview

A live preview tool for Atom Editor.

Install:
```bash
apm install atom-html-preview
```

Toogle HTML Preview:

Press `CTRL-P` in editor to open Preview.

readme:
# Atom HTML Preview

A live preview tool for Atom Editor.

Install:
```bash
apm install atom-html-preview
```

Toggle HTML Preview:

Press `CTRL-SHIFT-H` in the editor to open the preview pane.
